{"tid":1961997,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"劉怡翔寸嘴拒答CSI口罩去向","createTime":"2020-04-07T07:16:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T07:58:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0b1e3930dbec63873ca1b37743ada638c6f4559d","tid":1961997,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T07:16:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200407/PZYCPZSIRLACCILLLBSZSN62WU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200407%2FPZYCPZSIRLACCILLLBSZSN62WU%2F&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2lezWqReVd2N9LFFOFvvIGphw%3D&h=fe5ff77b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200407%2FPZYCPZSIRLACCILLLBSZSN62WU%2F&h=946ba506\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200407/PZYCPZSIRLACCILLLBSZSN62WU/</a><br />\n<br />\n劉怡翔寸嘴拒答CSI口罩去向<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200407/large/1586190557_e0a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200407%2Flarge%2F1586190557_e0a6.jpg&h=2d36b7eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉怡翔昨拒絕交代CSi口罩分發問題。朱永倫攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】立法會特別財務委員會會議上，財經事務及庫務局局長劉怡翔被議員追問政府CSI口罩的分發情況，劉以為免影響政府採購時的議價能力為由拒絕交代。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨郭家麒斥劉怡翔「離晒譜」，指申訴專員亦質疑政府規管CSI口罩的分發有問題，其間劉怡翔「寸嘴」回應：「唔知議員想要soundbite，定想我答問題呢？」<br />\n<br />\n民主派朱凱廸發言時主動反擊劉怡翔：「我先畀個soundbite局長先，我認為你唔答採購口罩分配咗邊個部門，唔係擔心損害政府議價能力，而係唔想警務處尷尬，呢個係我畀你嘅soundbite」；劉怡翔回應指朱猜測政府隱瞞部門資料，「呢個係完全無基礎」。<br />\n<br />\n早前有報道曾指在CSI口罩供應緊張，清潔及醫護人員獲派口罩不足之時，警隊卻獲發大量口罩，不少CSI口罩更流出市民高價發售；申訴署早前已表明會追查CSI口罩外流問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鄺俊宇質疑政府「做緊水魚」<br />\n<br />\n民主黨鄺俊宇則指出，據立法會行管會提供資料，行管會正以每個4.6元價錢以公帑購入口罩，查詢政府以有關價錢購入口罩是否合理，並質疑：「你係攞緊公帑，唔係你自己攞錢出嚟買口罩畀香港人呀，你幾時先披露林鄭買緊幾多錢口罩？令大家可以評估政府係咪做緊水魚？」劉怡翔聞言即說政府會在疫情過後披露相關資料，結果遭鄺批評「疫情過後，蚊都瞓！」其後又指坊間不乏貴過250元一盒的50個裝口罩，「我唔覺得我哋做咗愚蠢決定」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者林俊謙"},{"pid":"acb90caed2ad2eec60a8587892c1969dddd71372","tid":1961997,"uid":4783,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T07:25:47.000Z","msg":"佢係咪以為自己好醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4d6098a0932f62683e8b65651493d914df6fc6c","tid":1961997,"uid":442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"acb90caed2ad2eec60a8587892c1969dddd71372","tid":1961997,"uid":4783,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T07:25:47.000Z","msg":"佢係咪以為自己好醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T07:28:39.000Z","msg":"比人串完發夢之後放棄人生<br />\n等升職啦咁撚廢"},{"pid":"f37dfc7e86fa51f06e2ad6cb7451c9cff443b002","tid":1961997,"uid":34410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T07:32:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大部份文職既政府部門都係只可以獲派好薄既印尼sensi口罩<br />\nd csi 去左邊呢? <br />\n利申:日日拎緊垃圾sensi"},{"pid":"c42a8f7658ec539563ae24f3650a44413abd6909","tid":1961997,"uid":261873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T07:34:38.000Z","msg":"中已送"},{"pid":"db6555bef40d42399c626dab8c6eecbba7e812f0","tid":1961997,"uid":66898,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f37dfc7e86fa51f06e2ad6cb7451c9cff443b002","tid":1961997,"uid":34410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T07:32:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大部份文職既政府部門都係只可以獲派好薄既印尼sensi口罩<br />\nd csi 去左邊呢? <br />\n利申:日日拎緊垃圾sensi"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T07:37:07.000Z","msg":"利申:用緊垃圾sensi<br />\n真係好似紙咁薄, 最入最出個層 重要係薄到透明咁款"},{"pid":"fe21e5569789dc6cca75c555d42001cc57e05792","tid":1961997,"uid":190333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db6555bef40d42399c626dab8c6eecbba7e812f0","tid":1961997,"uid":66898,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f37dfc7e86fa51f06e2ad6cb7451c9cff443b002","tid":1961997,"uid":34410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20